summary: This small mod adds a new free player home nearby Riverwood
descriptionHtml:
Riverwood Hovel - Player Home
=========================

This small mod adds a new free players home nearby Riverwood, the home is called Riverwood Hovel, its just a small home for an Adventurer or Hunter, i will be working on adding Plaques and Mannequin in the near future, i hope you enjoy this small home, and it will be updated in time, thank you :)

=========================
V1.2
- Added Blacksmiths Forge
- Added Chopping Wood Block
- Added Outside Candles

V1.1 
- Added MapMarker (Riverwood Hovel)
- Added Alchemy Stand in Porch
- Added Walls around trees
author: WeazelHead
